      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FIRETHORN (5) is an accomplished stayer with a great record at the longer races. Scored over 660m at this track last time in a NG (37.97). Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of three starts. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. MIDNIGHT QUEEN (1) is an honest type in the frame at 23 of 55 starts including last time when third (38.04) over 660m at this track. Solid record at this trip including three wins. Best form too dangerous to ignore. Have to include. GOLDSTAR PRADA (7) has a strong record this trip with 12 wins and nine placings from 27 starts. Placed last time (38.03) at this track in a NG, finishing second and beaten 0.8 lengths. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. APACHE TIGER (8) racing over this distance brings the best out in him.",
